   297	  rather than CDN-loaded so the UI works offline / in CI without
   298	  external network.
   299	- `tests/__init__.py`
   300	- `tests/test_app.py` — `TestClient`-driven unit tests against
   301	  `make_app(store=InMemoryStore(...), …)`. Covers each route's
   302	  rendering and validation in isolation: GET / returns 200, GET
   303	  /planner lists pending plan tasks, malformed POST returns 400,
